@scolapasta before changing this one and the rest below in r-rapache-tworavens.rst I'd like to check with @djbrooke and @landreev about the plan for maintaining this "How to install TwoRavens" documentation. We don't even use Two Ravens ourselves anymore.
As I wrote under "Special notes for your reviewer",
'In the Installation Guide, should we delete the old Two Ravens content? I put a note saying "Please note that in the text below, Glassfish was changed to Payara but not tested."'

